  <h1>Oh no!</h1>
  <p>It seems you have encountered a 500: Internal Server Error!</p>
  <br>
  <h3>Don't fret:</h3>
  <p>Just go into your command line and type <code>tarbell config</code>.</p>
  <p>This will allow you to reconfigure your Google Spreadhseet so that your project can find it!</p>
  <br>
  <br>
  <h4>For the pros:</h4>
  <p>You can go into your <code>tarbell_config.py</code> file and make sure the <code>SPREADSHEET_KEY</code> matches the key in the URL of your project's Google Spreadsheet.</p>
  <p>It's the long string of letters and numbers after <code>?key=</code> and before the <code>&usp</code>.</p>
